name: Salesforce Marketing Cloud
description: Add a Salesforce Marketing Cloud Instance to connect your existing Salesforce Marketing Cloud account to the Marketing Hub, allowing you to manage activities, campaigns, and contacts across multiple Marketing Elements and other Salesforce services. You will need your Salesforce Marketing Cloud account information to add an instance.

configuration.name: SFDC Marketing Cloud Instance Name or Subdomain
configuration.description: The Salesforce Marketing Cloud instance name for legacy implementations, i.e. s1, s4, s6, s7. For v2 implementations, provide the subdomain of the tenant, which can connect to all instances. This can be found in your URL after logging into Salesforce Marketing Cloud, i.e. mc88d-g11f3n5hfbx18zj78zm4wq.
